    "content": "-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n\t         \"ONLY WANNA BE WITH YOU\" - Hootie & The Blowfish\r\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n\r\nTabbed By : Superkisseler\r\n\r\nTuning: Standard\r\n\r\nAs one of the few people who enjoy other songs by Hootie & The Blowfish except this one \r\nstill do love this one and this is my version of the tab.\r\n\r\nKEY:\r\n/ = SLIDE\r\n\r\nYou don't play in the beginning except for this:\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|-------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|---5---5-----------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nE|-------------------------------------------------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\nRest of the Song:\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|-------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|---4-4-4-4/---7-7-7-7----------------------------------------------------|\r\nE|-------------------------------------------------------------------------|[/tab]",
